- The metadata includes the date the image was taken, the archive date, and the primary and secondary genres.

sql:
SELECT name, corporate_type
FROM corporate_names
WHERE corporate_type IS NOT NULL;

SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM images) AS image_count,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM corporate_names) AS corporate_name_count;

